# Repo-wide default owner. Branch protection requires code-owner review on every pull request;
# this catch-all is what makes that apply to the whole repository, not just the paths named below.
* @angroene

# Code ownership for the documentation system. Changes under these paths request a review from the
# documentation maintainer. Listed for clarity even though it currently names the same owner as
# the catch-all above -- CODEOWNERS uses last-match-wins, so a future change to this section could
# name a different documentation maintainer without touching the repo-wide default.

# The documentation site and its build tooling.
/agentforge4j-docs/            @angroene

# The Java tooling that feeds the generated reference and the API surface.
/agentforge4j-docs-emitter/    @angroene
/agentforge4j-docs-javadoc/    @angroene

# The documentation CI and deployment workflows, and the shared build pipeline they consume.
/.github/workflows/docs.yml           @angroene
/.github/workflows/deploy.yml         @angroene
/.github/actions/build-docs-site/     @angroene
